data.description: Nestled in a sought-after community, this three bedroom, two bathroom residence boasts a generously sized living room with distinctive beam ceilings, exuding character and warmth. The expansive floor plan offers flexibility, making it an ideal space for a growing family. An attached garage provides convenient storage or parking, while the sizable yard promises endless opportunities for recreation, gardening, or family gatherings. Situated in a friendly and established neighborhood, this home is an invitation to both comfort and community.
